1.1-beta.1 (May 1, 2026)
- Migrates BN Reminders functionality and reminder data into BNX, consolidating reminder settings and email customization into the core BNX experience (MD-90, MD-104).
- Migrates lock settings controls from bnx_locksettings into BNX and absorbs the legacy sidecar configuration into BNX defaults (MD-107).
- Refactors mod form header label overrides into a reusable helper to simplify BNX-driven form customizations (MD-100).
- Adds a shared developer debug helper for BNX sidecars.

1.0.1 (April 1, 2026)
- Adds a BNX-specific guest access endpoint (guest.php) with its own join form, URL builder, and logout redirect flow, replacing the core guest page in BNX contexts (GIT-1).
- Hides BBB server setup instructions in the activity settings when credentials are pre-configured (MD-98).
- Improves recordings table UX (MD-94).
- Supports auto-set default settings decoupled from sidecars (MD-95, MD-97).

1.0 (March 11, 2026)
- First stable open-source release of bbbext_bnx.
- Introduces the BNX Framework: BigBlueButton BN Experience is a foundational UX enhancement extension for BigBlueButton in Moodle, featuring moderator approval workflows and shared capabilities that power the BNX extension family.
- Adds PreSession lobby access which replaces Wait for Moderator.
- Delivers an enhanced recording experience by improving the room recordings table and ensuring recording features work end-to-end.

0.1.0-beta.1 (March 11, 2026)
- Introduces the BNX Framework: BigBlueButton BN Experience is a foundational UX enhancement extension for BigBlueButton in Moodle, featuring moderator approval workflows and shared capabilities that power the BNX extension family.
- Adds PreSession lobby access which replaces Wait for Moderator.
